<!-- ============================================ 
  Síntesis de la lección (discusión de cierre)
=================================================  -->
<subsubsection xml:id="lec-masPracticaEnRepresentarYResolver-sintesis" component="profesor">
  <shorttitle><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></shorttitle>
  <title><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></title>
  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>(10 mins)</title>

  <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p><q>Hoy aprendimos la rutina ‘Falta de información’. ¿Cómo les ayudó esta rutina a darle sentido a los problemas que resolvieron?</q> (The routine gave me a chance to focus on what was important in the problem. I had to think about what I needed to know to solve the problem. I had to think about why some information was needed to solve the problem. It helped me make sense of what was happening in the problem.) </p>

</subsubsection>



